{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"The recent debate over copyright laws"},{"time":2000,"text":"like SOPA in the United States"},{"time":4000,"text":"and the ACTA agreement in Europe"},{"time":6000,"text":"has been very emotional."},{"time":8000,"text":"And I think some dispassionate, quantitative reasoning"},{"time":11000,"text":"could really bring a great deal to the debate."},{"time":13000,"text":"I'd therefore like to propose"},{"time":15000,"text":"that we employ, we enlist,"},{"time":17000,"text":"the cutting edge field of copyright math"},{"time":19000,"text":"whenever we approach this subject."}]},{"cues":[{"time":21000,"text":"For instance, just recently"},{"time":23000,"text":"the Motion Picture Association revealed"},{"time":25000,"text":"that our economy loses 58 billion dollars a year"},{"time":28000,"text":"to copyright theft."},{"time":31000,"text":"Now rather than just argue about this number,"},{"time":33000,"text":"a copyright mathematician will analyze it"},{"time":36000,"text":"and he'll soon discover that this money"},{"time":38000,"text":"could stretch from this auditorium"},{"time":40000,"text":"all the way across Ocean Boulevard"},{"time":42000,"text":"to the Westin, and then to Mars ..."},{"time":45000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":47000,"text":"... if we use pennies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":50000,"text":"Now this is obviously a powerful,"},{"time":52000,"text":"some might say dangerously powerful, insight."},{"time":55000,"text":"But it's also a morally important one."},{"time":57000,"text":"Because this isn't just the hypothetical retail value"},{"time":60000,"text":"of some pirated movies that we're talking about,"},{"time":62000,"text":"but this is actual economic losses."},{"time":64000,"text":"This is the equivalent"},{"time":66000,"text":"to the entire American corn crop failing"},{"time":68000,"text":"along with all of our fruit crops,"},{"time":71000,"text":"as well as wheat, tobacco,"},{"time":73000,"text":"rice, sorghum --"},{"time":75000,"text":"whatever sorghum is -- losing sorghum."}]},{"cues":[{"time":79000,"text":"But identifying the actual losses to the economy"},{"time":82000,"text":"is almost impossible to do"},{"time":84000,"text":"unless we use copyright math."},{"time":86000,"text":"Now music revenues are down by about eight billion dollars a year"},{"time":89000,"text":"since Napster first came on the scene."},{"time":91000,"text":"So that's a chunk of what we're looking for."},{"time":94000,"text":"But total movie revenues"},{"time":96000,"text":"across theaters, home video and pay-per-view are up."},{"time":98000,"text":"And TV, satellite and cable revenues are way up."},{"time":101000,"text":"Other content markets like book publishing and radio"},{"time":103000,"text":"are also up."},{"time":105000,"text":"So this small missing chunk here"},{"time":107000,"text":"is puzzling."}]},{"cues":[{"time":109000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":112000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":115000,"text":"Since the big content markets"},{"time":117000,"text":"have grown in line with historic norms,"},{"time":119000,"text":"it's not additional growth that piracy has prevented,"},{"time":122000,"text":"but copyright math tells us"},{"time":124000,"text":"it must therefore be foregone growth"},{"time":127000,"text":"in a market that has no historic norms --"},{"time":129000,"text":"one that didn't exist in the 90's."},{"time":131000,"text":"What we're looking at here"},{"time":133000,"text":"is the insidious cost of ringtone piracy."},{"time":135000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":139000,"text":"50 billion dollars of it a year,"},{"time":141000,"text":"which is enough, at 30 seconds a ringtone,"},{"time":143000,"text":"that could stretch from here"},{"time":145000,"text":"to Neanderthal times."},{"time":147000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":151000,"text":"It's true."},{"time":153000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":155000,"text":"I have Excel."}]},{"cues":[{"time":157000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":159000,"text":"The movie folks also tell us"},{"time":161000,"text":"that our economy loses"},{"time":163000,"text":"over 370,000 jobs to content theft,"},{"time":166000,"text":"which is quite a lot when you consider that, back in '98,"},{"time":169000,"text":"the Bureau of Labor Statistics indicated"},{"time":171000,"text":"that the motion picture and video industries"},{"time":173000,"text":"were employing 270,000 people."},{"time":176000,"text":"Other data has the music industry at about 45,000 people."},{"time":179000,"text":"And so the job losses that came with the Internet"},{"time":181000,"text":"and all that content theft,"},{"time":183000,"text":"have therefore left us with negative employment in our content industries."},{"time":186000,"text":"And this is just one of the many mind-blowing statistics"},{"time":189000,"text":"that copyright mathematicians have to deal with every day."},{"time":191000,"text":"And some people think that string theory is tough."}]},{"cues":[{"time":194000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":196000,"text":"Now this is a key number from the copyright mathematicians' toolkit."},{"time":199000,"text":"It's the precise amount of harm"},{"time":201000,"text":"that comes to media companies"},{"time":203000,"text":"whenever a single copyrighted song or movie"},{"time":205000,"text":"gets pirated."},{"time":207000,"text":"Hollywood and Congress derived this number mathematically"},{"time":210000,"text":"back when they last sat down to improve copyright damages"},{"time":213000,"text":"and made this law."},{"time":215000,"text":"Some people think this number's a little bit large,"},{"time":217000,"text":"but copyright mathematicians who are media lobby experts"},{"time":220000,"text":"are merely surprised"},{"time":222000,"text":"that it doesn't get compounded for inflation every year."}]},{"cues":[{"time":225000,"text":"Now when this law first passed,"},{"time":227000,"text":"the world's hottest MP3 player could hold just 10 songs."},{"time":230000,"text":"And it was a big Christmas hit."},{"time":232000,"text":"Because what little hoodlum wouldn't want"},{"time":234000,"text":"a million and a half bucks-worth of stolen goods in his pocket."}]},{"cues":[{"time":236000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":239000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":244000,"text":"These days an iPod Classic can hold 40,000 songs,"},{"time":247000,"text":"which is to say eight billion dollars-worth"},{"time":250000,"text":"of stolen media."},{"time":252000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":254000,"text":"Or about 75,000 jobs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":256000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":258000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":263000,"text":"Now you might find copyright math strange,"},{"time":266000,"text":"but that's because it's a field"},{"time":268000,"text":"that's best left to experts."},{"time":270000,"text":"So that's it for now."},{"time":272000,"text":"I hope you'll join me next time"},{"time":274000,"text":"when I will be making an equally scientific and fact-based inquiry"},{"time":277000,"text":"into the cost of alien music piracy to he American economy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":280000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":282000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":284000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":286000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}